README
======

1. About
--------

This is the source code for debcite, a citation retrieval engine to make retrieving evidence 
from the public wiki for intercollegiate policy debates easier and more efficient. It parses 
shorthand citations and uses a variety of techniques, including the Google and Yahoo search 
APIs, to try to retrieve the full text of the evidence being cited.

It's written in PHP and JavaScript with MySQL, and the primary implementation is at 
http://www.jpwright.net/debcite

